headlines.description: — Miami was desperate. So was Dallas.
headlines.shortLinkText: Butler has 35, Miami gets needed win over Dallas, 129-122

events.name: LA Clippers at New Orleans Pelicans

headlines.description: — When Clippers star Kawhi Leonard hit big shots in the closing minutes, the Pelicans answered with Brandon Ingram, whose recent form has sent his team surging up the standings.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ingram's 36 points lead Pelicans past Clippers, 122-114
